488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8xVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=295a994c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8xVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=36943da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8xVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=355118ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d641a5be3b6b8ce1e37f9a6c9706197b7f6e5159","tid":1744443,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:51:09.000Z","msg":"屈機"}]}